Tucker Salovaara and Edwin Munet

MTEC 2280

Text Adventure Script



You are in the train and the power goes out. Press 1. to go to the intercom or 2 to sit down and cry.
1.You are at the intercom and talk to the conductor.
2.You lose.
Conductor says go to the emergency window and open it. Press 1. Dont listen press 2. go to window
1. You trip and die 
2. You climb out the window and find an emergency exit.
Emergency exit is right here but other people are still stuck. Press 1. Help them press 2. screw them
1. You are a hero
2.Basatard they all died good job getting the bad end.
